screen_desc:
The screenshot shows a ride-hailing app interface where the user is reserving a ride. The pickup location is set to "Washington Hilton," and the destination field is empty. Below, there is a list of saved places, including:

1. Virginia Hospital Center, 1701 N George Mason Dr, Arlington, VA
2. Marriott, 901 Massachusetts Ave NW, Washington, DC
3. Omni Shoreham Hotel, 2500 Calvert St NW, Washington, DC
4. Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport, 1 Aviation Cir, Arlington, VA
5. Washington Hilton, 1919 Connecticut Ave NW, Washington, DC

The keyboard at the bottom of the screen is active, showing a custom theme with a background image of a tent under a starry sky. The time displayed at the top of the screen is 8:53 AM, and various status icons are visible, including battery, signal strength, and notifications.
